{"tid":671451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[何君堯]暴動案陪審員被拍攝　陳曼琪：佔中破窗效應","createTime":"2018-05-20T06:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T10:05:59.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e44dadbefaae5e1ed319998ab2dd45dd95a313","tid":671451,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:57:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D-%E9%99%B3%E6%9B%BC%E7%90%AA-%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E7%A0%B4%E7%AA%97%E6%95%88%E6%87%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%259B%25BC%25E7%2590%25AA-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%25AA%2597%25E6%2595%2588%25E6%2587%2589%2F&d=nDvskFM%2FCnaCO%2FvNG493cv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b96300d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E9%2599%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%259B%25BC%25E7%2590%25AA-%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E7%25AA%2597%25E6%2595%2588%25E6%2587%2589%2F&h=6391fa4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88%E9%99%AA%E5%AF%A9%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D-%E9%99%B3%E6%9B%BC%E7%90%AA-%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%AD%E7%A0%B4%E7%AA%97%E6%95%88%E6%87%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n本民前前發言人梁天琦等五人的暴動罪審訊案，審訊過程中發生多次在法庭內拍攝陪審員的事件。在陪審員裁決前，司法機構更收到附有4名陪審員的電郵，寫有「還有很多&hellip;.」疑似威脅的內容。港區人大代表、反佔中律師陳曼琪昨日回應，形容事件是「佔中破窗效應」。<br />\n<br />\n陳曼琪就事件接受了親建制媒體《港人講地》的訪問，認為拍攝陪審員及電郵至司法機關等行為，是涉嫌藐視法庭及妨礙司法公正，性質非常嚴重，須予以最強烈的譴責。<br />\n<br />\n陳曼琪在FB轉載了自己的訪問，並進一步撰文回應事件，認為有關行為是與佔中有關：「『佔中破窗效應』令到一些人覺得只要夠膽挑戰法律、挑戰法庭命令就無事。這些情況必須加以嚴懲，以儆效尤。」<br />\n<br />\n今年三月，法庭處理梁天琦一案時，有懷疑內地男遊客利用手機拍攝法庭內情況，拍攝角度更疑似朝着陪審團方向，更有公眾人士指看到男遊客透過微信發送照片。<br />\n<br />\n至上周五主審法官彭寶琴開庭表示，法庭接獲司法機構行政部同事通知，收到有人發附有4名陪審員的照片去司法機構投訴辦事處，電郵內容寫上「還有很多&hellip;.」，故提議下令公眾人士不得進入庭內聽審。"},{"pid":"246e7a9637fa39347b7c60f51ab6e02f8bea256b","tid":671451,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e0580c29c53d0a2aa7340edbb26c67aff431fc","tid":671451,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"鄭裕丹屋企被偷野都係受佔中影響"},{"pid":"0e3e17a7bd8ea8e09f8bb0e535623afdecb3b482","tid":671451,"uid":54516,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"屈穎妍2.0"},{"pid":"12c70745eaeb427c3a85c8bc43e3ab63086e6fc9","tid":671451,"uid":27688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"76e0580c29c53d0a2aa7340edbb26c67aff431fc","tid":671451,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"鄭裕丹屋企被偷野都係受佔中影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"我隔離屋隻狗便秘都係受佔中影響"},{"pid":"7b38dfe27991cb0b249fe866f639c8cc57c39d3d","tid":671451,"uid":49918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:21:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fe700bca9f57827d59e305cee2c6a41fee37ef2","tid":671451,"uid":61271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:22:31.000Z","msg":"律政司僭建都係因為佔中"},{"pid":"5956de549c6f8473856379c74f75aace96fa2a54","tid":671451,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"7436f9819d5a0486be96471dad44ad4c79677580","tid":671451,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"我男鄰居嘅姑媽扭親條腰都關佔鐘事"},{"pid":"f711271f516421666772a952afac05781316ba18","tid":671451,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T